profile:
Greyhorne Interiors is Ottawa's newest modern furniture store.  From solid walnut dining tables to down-filled sofas, they have what you need to fill your contemporary space.

Owner James Flynn opened Greyhorne as a means of bringing high-end designer furniture to Ottawa. "You won't find salespeople here, just real people who love good design", say James.
Each piece they carry is fully customizable to suit your needs in your choice of wood species and size to your preference of leather or fabric.  
Every brand is carefully selected from Team 7 in Austria, Artifort from Holland, or Carl Hansen and Eilersen from Denmark.  All pieces are authentic designs from the best craftspeople the world has ever seen.

Price range - Medium to High

http://www.greyhorne.com

Fibrenew Outaouais / Gatineau specializes in the repair, restoration and renewal of leather, plastics, vinyl, fabric and upholstery servicing six major markets: automotive, aviation, commercial, medical, marine and residential. Utilizing our services to repair damaged materials in your vehicle, boat, airplane, home or office offers an environmentally-friendly and cost-effective alternative to replacement.

Leather Repair, Vinyl Restoration and Plastic Renewal Services in:
Gatineau, Quebec; Aylmer, Quebec; Buckingham, Quebec; Cantley, Quebec; La Peche, Quebec; Chelsea, Quebec; Maniwaki, Quebec; Saint-Andre-Avellin, Quebec; Thurso, Quebec
